<template>

              <small class="text-muted">Last activity: {{ printDate() }}</small>

</template>

<script>
// @ is an alias to /src
// import HelloWorld from '@/components/HelloWorld.vue'
// import NavbarPage from '@/components/NavbarPage.vue'
//  import { mdbBtn } from 'mdbvue';
//  import api from '../api';

export default {
  name: 'user',
  components: {
    //  mdbBtn,
  },
  data () {
    return {
      user: {}
    }
  },
  mounted () {
    this.user = this.$route.params.body
    if(this.$route.params.body === undefined || this.$route.params.body === null){
      this.$route.push('/')
    }
  },
  methods: {
    printDate () {
      console.log('sa')
      if (this.user.last_activity.days_ago !== 0) {
        return this.user.last_activity.days_ago + ' day' + (this.user.last_activity.days_ago > 1 ? 's' : '') + ' ago'
      }
      else if (this.user.last_activity.hours_ago !== 0) {
        return this.user.last_activity.hours_ago + ' hour' + (this.user.last_activity.hours_ago > 1 ? 's' : '') + ' ago'
      }
      else if (this.user.last_activity.minutes_ago !== 0) {
        return this.user.last_activity.minutes_ago + ' minute' + (this.user.last_activity.minutes_ago > 1 ? 's' : '') + ' ago'
      }
      else {
        return this.user.last_activity.seconds_ago + ' second' + (this.user.last_activity.seconds_ago > 1 ? 's' : '') + ' ago'
      }
    }
  }
}
</script>
